) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"480px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-family-handyman.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-family-handyman.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" sizes=\"480px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-family-handyman.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <img class=\" lazyloaded\" alt=\"home-improvement-websites-family-handyman\" \/> <\/picture><\/figure><\/div><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The knowledge areas are broken down by categories: rooms of the house (e.g. attic, kitchen, bedroom), parts of the house (e.g. walls, ceilings, doors), home maintenance skills (e.g. electrical, carpentry, plumbing), and outdoor skills (e.g. garden, decks, patio).<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">What I like best is that each article is dedicated to solving a singular problem, like &#8220;How to Prevent Bathroom Mold&#8221;. It makes it easy to search through the site for the exact projects and improvements that you need for your own home.<\/span><\/p><div class=\"ad-even\">\u00a0<\/div><h2 id=\"remodelaholic\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.remodelaholic.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Remodelaholic<\/a><\/h2><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Remodelaholic<\/strong> is the place to go if you want to do\u00a0<a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.muo.com\/tag\/3d-design-daily-life-plan-home-diy-project-sketchup\/\">DIY home renovation<\/a> on a budget. The author&#8217;s motto is &#8220;Reduce, Reuse, Recycle, Repurpose, Remodel&#8221; and you can really see it come to life in every single project they undertake.<\/span><\/p><div class=\"body-img responsive-img img-article-item\"><figure><picture> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 1024px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"750px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" sizes=\"750px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 768px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 768px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"943px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" sizes=\"943px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 481px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 481px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"767px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" sizes=\"767px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 0px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 0px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"480px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" sizes=\"480px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <img class=\" lazyloaded\" alt=\"home-improvement-websites-remodelaholic\" \/> <\/picture><\/figure><\/div><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The best part? Their tight budget is an annual $5,000 for their entire home. If you&#8217;ve ever done <em>any<\/em> home remodeling, you&#8217;d know that that isn&#8217;t much of a budget at all \u2014 yet they make it work. Who says that fixing up a home has to cost an arm and a leg?<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">New posts are made at a rapid pace (sometimes multiple times a day) so you&#8217;ll never run out of content to consume or find ideas for your next project.<\/span><\/p><h2 id=\"diy-network\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.diynetwork.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DIY Network<\/a><\/h2><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Let&#8217;s say you&#8217;re new to the whole idea of home improvement, but you aren&#8217;t working under any money constraints. All you want is expert advice from expert renovators. For that, you should really check out <strong>DIY Network<\/strong>.<\/span><\/p><div class=\"body-img responsive-img img-article-item\"><figure><picture> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 1024px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"750px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" sizes=\"750px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 768px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 768px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"943px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" sizes=\"943px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 481px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 481px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"767px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" sizes=\"767px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 0px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 0px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"480px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" sizes=\"480px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-diynetwork.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <img class=\" lazyloaded\" alt=\"home-improvement-websites-diynetwork\" \/> <\/picture><\/figure><\/div><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">DIY Network comes from the same people behind the Food Network and HGTV, so you know that they have the pull and power to bring in advice and wisdom from the best of the best. To be clear, it&#8217;s primarily a television channel (available worldwide) but the website is full of great information.<\/span><\/p><div class=\"ad-even\">\u00a0<\/div><h2 id=\"ikea-hackers\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.ikeahackers.net\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">IKEA Hackers<\/a><\/h2><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">IKEA gets a lot of hate \u2014 I&#8217;m never sure if it&#8217;s genuine hatred or just one big inside joke that spans the world \u2014 but I love it. Sure, you get what you pay for when you buy the cheapest of IKEA&#8217;s offerings, but their mid and upper-tier products aren&#8217;t bad at all.<\/span><\/p><div class=\"body-img responsive-img img-article-item\"><figure><picture> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 1024px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"750px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" sizes=\"750px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 768px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 768px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"943px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" sizes=\"943px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 481px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 481px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"767px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" sizes=\"767px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 0px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 0px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"480px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" sizes=\"480px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <img class=\" lazyloaded\" alt=\"home-improvement-websites-ikea-hackers\" \/> <\/picture><\/figure><\/div><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">But if you don&#8217;t share my sentiment, maybe this will change your mind: <strong>IKEA Hackers<\/strong> is a website dedicated to IKEA product modifications (such as this\u00a0<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.muo.com\/tag\/how-to-build-a-cheap-standing-desk-from-ikea-and-what-its-like-to-use\/\">IKEA-based standing desk<\/a>) <span style=\"color: #000000;\">and improvements that don&#8217;t require much money. With a bit of elbow grease, you can have amazing furniture for dirt cheap.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">To get an idea of what it&#8217;s about, visit the<\/span>\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/www.ikeahackers.net\/start-here\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Start Here<\/a> <span style=\"color: #000000;\">page, check out the collection of &#8220;easy peasy done-in-an-afternoon&#8221; projects, and try a few of them. Don&#8217;t be surprised if you become an IKEA fan by the end!<\/span><\/p><div class=\"ad-odd\">\u00a0<\/div><h2 id=\"r-homeimprovement\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.reddit.com\/r\/homeimprovement\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\/r\/HomeImprovement<\/a><\/h2><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">As they say, &#8220;there&#8217;s a subreddit for everything&#8221; and the subject of home improvement is no exception. New to Reddit? Don&#8217;t worry.<\/span> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.muo.com\/tag\/how-to-use-reddit\/\">Learning all about Reddit<\/a> <span style=\"color: #000000;\">is easy, but once you do you&#8217;ll wonder how you got by without it.<\/span><\/p><div class=\"body-img responsive-img img-article-item\"><figure><picture> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 1024px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"750px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" sizes=\"750px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=750&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 768px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 768px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"943px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" sizes=\"943px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=943&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 481px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 481px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"767px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" sizes=\"767px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=767&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 0px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 0px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" sizes=\"480px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <source srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" sizes=\"480px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static1.makeuseofimages.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/02\/home-improvement-websites-reddit.png?q=50&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=480&amp;dpr=1.5\" \/> <img class=\" lazyloaded\" alt=\"home-improvement-websites-reddit\" \/> <\/picture><\/figure><\/div><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The community of <strong>\/r\/HomeImprovement<\/strong> is a fantastic resource for newbies. It&#8217;s more of a place to ask questions and request advice than it is a place to discuss the intricacies of home improvement, though the latter does happen sometimes.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">And if you hate product advertisements and endorsements, you&#8217;ll love it here since the moderators ban all product links (except for ones that were specifically requested).<\/span><\/p><h2 id=\"get-started-on-your-home\">Get Started on Your\u00a0Home<\/h2><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Whether it&#8217;s as simple as painting a door or as involved as splitting a room into two, home improvement projects exist for every level of the skill spectrum. Even if you have absolutely no experience, there&#8217;s still <em>something<\/em> you can do right now. Seriously, <em>right now<\/em>!<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Would you rather put up with an unsatisfying home? Or spend a bit time and energy making it into a place that makes you smile when you walk through the entrance? It&#8217;s an easy answer, if you ask me.<\/span><\/p><\/section>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Phone (469) 612-0186 Remodel Your Home: 6 Websites for Learning the Basics Would you rather put up with an unsatisfying home? Or spend a bit time and energy making it into a place that makes you smile when you walk through the entrance? There are few things worse than a home that&#8217;s&nbsp;falling apart at the [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":1456,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"ocean_post_layout":"","ocean_both_sidebars_style":"","ocean_both_sidebars_content_width":0,"oce